\ 1+ ( n -- n+1 ), 1- ( n -- n-1 ), sq ( n -- n*n ) — float-only fast paths.

\ basic
5 1+ . cr             \ 6
5 1- . cr             \ 4
5 sq . cr             \ 25

\ composes
3 1+ sq . cr          \ 16
10 sq 1- . cr         \ 99
0 1- 1- 1- . cr       \ -3

\ floats with fractions
0.5 1+ . cr           \ 1.5
0.25 sq . cr          \ 0.0625

\ inside a quotation, with times
[: | n | 0 to n  [: n 1+ to n :] 7 times  n . cr :] execute
